# 41. Complete CI/CD Workflow

The overall deployment lifecycle can be summarized as follows:

```
Developer
      │
      ▼
Git Push
      │
      ▼
GitHub Repository
      │
      ▼
Azure DevOps Pipeline
      │
      ├─────────────── CI ───────────────┐
      │                                  │
      ▼                                  ▼
Checkout → Restore → Build → Test → Publish → Artifact
                                           │
                                           ▼
                               Continuous Deployment
                                           │
                                           ▼
                             Download Artifact
                                           │
                                           ▼
                             Copy to AWS EC2
                                           │
                                           ▼
                              Stop Application
                                           │
                                           ▼
                                Create Backup
                                           │
                                           ▼
                               Deploy New Build
                                           │
                                           ▼
                             Start systemd Service
                                           │
                                           ▼
                                 Health Check
                                           │
                                           ▼
                               Deployment Complete
```

This workflow provides a fully automated, repeatable, and reliable software delivery process, reducing manual effort and minimizing deployment risks.
